<P>
   An outlet for adventuresome spirits
</P>
<P>
   A man rowing around the world. A family sailing the Pacific in a
44-foot sloop. A group on 16-foot Trimarans traveling from Japan to
Alaska across the Northern Pacific, and another circumnavigating
the world on bicycles and pedal boats. These are some of the real
life adventures brought to the Web by the Global Online Adventure
Learning Site, with daily reports and charts.
</P>
<P>
   www.goals.com
