<P>
   Know a Georgia fan who wants to celebrate the win over Georgia
Southern, or has another special occasion coming up? Part of the
University of Georgia Athletic Association's official site is
dedicated to online greeting cards. Pick a card, fill in a personal
message, and e-mail it faster than you can say ``Go Dawgs.''
</P>
