</P>
<P>
   LA-LABOR (Los Angeles) _ On this Labor Day weekend, organized
labor can celebrate a growing number of card-carrying members in
Los Angeles, where janitors and home-care workers won significant
union battles during the past year. By Rick Orlov. (Will move in
the ``a'' national and ``n'' California news files.)
</P>
