   -- Jack McDowell's next start will be Wednesday night _ at the
Viper Room on Sunset Blvd.
</P>
<P>
   That's where Black Jack's band, Stickfigure, plays the first of
a buncha live performances around So Cal over the next few weeks.
The former splitfinger flinger takes center stage on vocals and
guitar. ...
</P>
<P>
   -- By the time he's 43, Bret Saberhagen's arm should be rested.
...
</P>
<P>
   -- Something's just wrong with baseball when Dante Bichette can
be traded on the last day of August and still be eligible for the
new team's playoff roster. ...
</P>
<P>
   -- Angels aren't gonna get Shiggy with it for much longer. ...
</P>
