<HEADLINE>
FOREIGN WORKERS AT HIGHEST LEVEL IN SEVEN DECADES
</HEADLINE>
  (Eds: SUBS 5th graf, ``Immigrants are ..., to correct first name to
Demetrios.) 
By STEVEN GREENHOUSE   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
